"major or minor release (see :doc:`Version Scheme </developer/releases"
"/version-scheme>`). The current release and past major releases are "
"always available on the `Downloads <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/downloads/>`__ page, while all ISOs, including past minor "
"releases, are available from our `download mirrors <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/downloads/#mirrors>`__."
